  <description><![CDATA[<p>Just a few minutes' walk from the lakefront and San Giovanni train station, Hotel Plinius is ideally located. It's central position within a pedestrian friendly area makes it the ideal base for travelling around Como as well as the other resorts on Italy's most luxurious lake. From Como, there is also the option to travel further afield to the likes of Milan and St Moritz on the train. The rooms here are traditionally furnished and offer a comfortable retreat at the end of the day. Breakfast can be enjoyed at the hotel where a good choice of continental options are available. For lunch and dinner, you'll find plenty of local eateries within easy walking distance.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 2 hours by coach from Milan Malpensa airport.</p>]]></description>
